# Welcome Modal System

## Overview

Bashcord includes a welcome modal system that greets new users and encourages them to join the Discord server. This system is integrated directly into the core Vencord initialization.

## Implementation

### Core Integration
The welcome system is integrated in [src/Vencord.ts](mdc:src/Vencord.ts):

```typescript
import { openWelcomeModal } from "./components/WelcomeModal";

// In init() function
setTimeout(() => {
    const hasShownWelcome = localStorage.getItem("bashcord-welcome-shown");
    
    if (!hasShownWelcome) {
        openWelcomeModal();
        localStorage.setItem("bashcord-welcome-shown", "true");
    }
}, 3000);
```

